## Install Z1+

Z1+ can be downloaded from the official repository: https://github.com/mkmat/Z1plus-code/tree/main.

is available here: https://github.com/mkmat/Z1plus-code/tree/main

To install the program, run:

```perl Z1+install/Z1+install.pl```

Make sure you have Perl installed on your system before running the installer.


## Entanglement calculation
### Step 1: Generate `config.Z1`
To prepare the input file required by Z1+, convert your LAMMPS trajectory using:

```perl ./Z1+import_lammps.pl -dump="droplet.lammpstraj" - data=droplet.data -ignore_H"```

Explanation of arguments:

-dump → LAMMPS trajectory file (.lammpstraj) \
-data → LAMMPS data file \
-ignore_H → excludes hydrogen atoms

### Step 2: Run Z1+
Once `config.Z1` is generated, run the entanglement analysis:

`./Z1+ config.Z1`
